# Random Fun Facts Generator

A simple, web application that displays random interesting facts. Built with [Pieces](https://pieces.app) for rapid development and code reuse.


## 🌟 Features

- Display random interesting facts
- Smooth fade-in animations
- Responsive design
- Clean, modern UI
- One-click fact generation

## 🚀 Live Demo

Check out the live application here: [Random Fun Facts Generator](https://linukaar.github.io/Fanfacts-Sri-Lanka-Pieces/)

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript
- JSON for data storage

